{
  "text": "However, personal values have been shown to act as predictors or moderators of business processes and results [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Personal values exert a strong influence in particular in small businesses, where the entrepreneurs' personal characteristics, their beliefs, attitudes and behavior largely determine the performance and business results, including innovation (Ajzen, 1991; [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
